      • addCountry

        private void addCountry(Pais country)
        Creates the form to create or edit a Country that will be inserted into the panel co. This form allows the user to give the country a name and its correspondent code. This method is really meticulous about the way it reads the input as it tests if the input matches the desired format.It will not accept until the user types something that matches the format.

      • addCompetition

        private void addCompetition()
        Creates the form to create a Competition that will be inserted into the panel di. This form allows the user to give the competition a name, to choose its correspondent sport. This method is really meticulous about the way it reads the input as it tests if the input matches the desired format.It will not accept until the user types something that matches the format.

      • addSport

        private void addSport()
        Creates the form to create a Sport that will be inserted into the panel spo. This form allows the user to give the sport a name. This method is really meticulous about the way it reads the input as it tests if the input matches the desired format.It will not accept until the user types something that matches the format.
